VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT ContentResolver\.query\(".*"\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:selectionArgs|bindArgs|\?,\s*arrayOf|validate|sanitize
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure usage of ContentResolver.query() method, which may lead to SQL injection vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Method Call: ContentResolver.query().
